2147.603","u": "Yes. Why did they not take the camera away?"},    {"who": "Yanusch Deutsch", "start": "2151.191","u": "That was not taken. Well, papers were taken away, yes, because they were also afraid of espionage."},    {"who": "David Boder", "start": "2159.718","u": "Yes."},    {"who": "Yanusch Deutsch", "start": "2161.327","u": "And we were there five, five hours. And then we were quickly, immediately in the railway cars. Then the cars were locked. From [unintelligible] within three minutes we were in a big city. Soldiers had come, German soldiers came [unintelligible], German soldiers. Big city, many people. And we were received. And soldiers and Red Cross Sisters and . . ."},    {"who": "David Boder", "start": "2199.281","u": "[interrupts] [unintelligible] Sister?"},    {"who": "Yanusch Deutsch", "start": "2201.965","u": "Very nice they were. And they led us into a waiting room. There were chairs. There, we saw a chair for the first time after two, after three or four months. And a lamp. And I was afraid to sit in a chair. I just wanted to sit on the earth, on the ground."},    {"who": "David Boder", "start": "2221.220","u": "Yes."},    {"who": "Yanusch Deutsch", "start": "2222.784","u": "And then we received food. First soup and then lighter things, then later chocolate [several words unintelligible]. Then we slowly, slowly understood that we have come to Switzerland and that we are saved."},    {"who": "David Boder", "start": "2241.315","u": "Your entire family?"},    {"who": "Yanusch Deutsch", "start": "2242.709","u": "Yes."},    {"who": "David Boder", "start": "2243.712","u": "And then, what happened in Switzerland?"},    {"who": "Yanusch Deutsch", "start": "2246.454","u": "In Switzerland we were in an &#34;Auffanglager&#34; [refugee camp] in Montreux. Was not very good. In another &#34;Auffanglager&#34; as well. Was for two months, for three months. And then I went to Engelberg, in an asylum. My mother was there, too. Was in an English Institute, was there for one year. In an English Institute."},    {"who": "David Boder", "start": "2271.206","u": "Are you still living in Engelberg?"},    {"who": "Yanusch Deutsch", "start": "2272.502","u": "Yes."},    {"who": "David Boder", "start": "2273.211","u": "And your father?"},    {"who": "Yanusch Deutsch", "start": "2274.150","u": "My father is in the Z&#195;rich area, working as an engineer."},    {"who": "David Boder", "start": "2277.322","u": "Yes. So, why can your mother not live with him?"},    {"who": "Yanusch Deutsch", "start": "2280.840","u": "Well, my, my father does not earn enough so that my mother can live there, too."},    {"who": "David Boder", "start": "2286.039","u": "I see. And in Z&#195;rich, he is with, with whom?"},    {"who": "Yanusch Deutsch", "start": "2290.476","u": "In a company, he works in a private company."},    {"who": "David Boder", "start": "2293.961","u": "I see. Well?"},    {"who": "Yanusch Deutsch", "start": "2295.648","u": "He is a very good professional."},    {"who": "David Boder", "start": "2297.299","u": "How far is Engelbrecht [mistaking the name] from here?"},    {"who": "Yanusch Deutsch", "start": "2300.788","u": "Engelberg is close to the Vierwaldst&#195;ttersee [Lake Lucerne]."},    {"who": "David Boder", "start": "2304.915","u": "In . . . ?"},    {"who": "Yanusch Deutsch", "start": "2305.167","u": "Do you know where Lucerne is at?"},    {"who": "David Boder", "start": "2307.160","u": "How far, eh, . . . ?"},    {"who": "Yanusch Deutsch", "start": "2308.675","u": "Three hundred kilometers from here."},    {"who": "David Boder", "start": "2310.629","u": "From here. Can one take the train to there?"},    {"who": "Yanusch Deutsch", "start": "2313.222","u": "Yes."},    {"who": "David Boder", "start": "2314.402","u": "Are there many people there?"},    {"who": "Yanusch Deutsch", "start": "2315.815","u": "It is a spa town. You know, one of the most beautiful spa towns in Switzerland. Has approximately one thousand inhabitants. But [u